! Init&Destory Func
DestroyFunc StartFunction
AddToFunc StartFunction         
+ I Module FvwmAuto 500 Raise Nop
+ I Module FvwmAnimate
+ I Module FvwmCommandS
+ I Module FvwmEvent
+ I Module FvwmScript
+ I Module FvwmEvent
+ I Module FvwmButtons FvwmTaskBar
+ I Exec exec ~/.screenlayout/screen_init.sh
+ I Exec exec ~/.fvwm/Utilities/ChangeWallpaper
+ I GenMenu "Programs"
+ I GenMenu "Utilities"
# + I Exec exec ~/.fvwm/dir-watch Programs &
# + I Exec exec ~/.fvwm/dir-watch Utilities &


DestroyFunc InitFunction
AddToFunc InitFunction    
+ I Exec exec xscreensaver -no-splash
# + I Exec exec xcompmgr & # -c -C -t-5 -l-5 -r4.2 -o.55 &
+ I Exec exec compton &
+ I Exec exec ibus-daemon -x -r -d
+ I Exec exec blueman-applet &
+ I Exec exec nm-applet &
DestroyFunc ExitFunction
AddToFunc ExitFunction
+ I All (xscreensaver) Close
+ I All (compton) Close
+ I All (ibus-daemon) Close

! Module
*FvwmAnimate: Delay 25
*FvwmAnimate: Effect Random
*FvwmAnimate: Width 3

