*FvwmTaskBar: Columns 1200

*FvwmTaskBar: (50x1, Title "Fvwm", ActiveColorset 16, Action(Mouse 1) \
               Menu RootMenu Root 0 o100-24p, Frame 2)
*FvwmTaskBar: (16x1, Icon "icons/terminal.svg:16x0" , ActiveColorset 16, \
               Action(Mouse 1) "Exec exec urxvt")
*FvwmTaskBar: (16x1, Icon "icons/google-chrome.svg:16x0", ActiveColorset 16, \
               Action(Mouse 1) "Exec exec google-chrome-stable")

*FvwmTaskBar: (1200x1, Left, Swallow TaskBarIcons 'Module FvwmIconMan \
               TaskBarIcons')
*FvwmTaskBar: (120x1, Swallow(NoClose, UseOld) stalonetray 'Exec exec stalonetray', Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (120x1, Swallow FvwmPager 'Module FvwmPager')
*FvwmTaskBar: (80x1, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript FvwmScript-Time', Frame 0))

